      "message": "Yes, but it\u0027s not directly related, since this is running in the adb liveness check.\nWhen booting from quickboot, the following would happen:\n\nemulator_details {\n  ...\n  quickboot_load {\n    state: EMULATOR_QUICKBOOT_LOAD_SUCCEEDED\n  }\n  snapshot_loads {\n    load_state: EMULATOR_SNAPSHOT_LOAD_SUCCEEDED_NORMAL\n  }\n}\n\nFollowed by the boot metrics:\n\nemulator_details {\n  boot_info {\n    boot_status: BOOT_COMPLETED\n    duration_ms: 2758\n  }\n}\n\n\nIf I load another snapshot, I will see another snapshot_loads, but not followed by another boot_info, because adb liveness checker already finds the image as booted up the first time.",
